# Titan client — build-time environment.
#
# These are PUBLIC values, safe to embed in a static client bundle:
#  - VITE_SUPABASE_URL      your project URL, e.g. https://abcd1234.supabase.co
#  - VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY the ANON public key (RLS protects all data; this key
#                           is designed to ship in clients). NEVER put the
#                           service_role key here or anywhere client-side.
#
# Leave them UNSET to build the zero-config live preview (the default landing).
# Set them to build/run the multiplayer client against your Supabase project.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# Only needed for GitHub Pages PROJECT sites served under /<repo>/.
# On Vercel/Netlify/custom domains served at root, leave this unset (defaults /).
# VITE_BASE=/your-repo-name/
